49:50.110 --> 49:51.225
With two other guys.

49:52.190 --> 49:54.351
- With guns.
- Shannon?

49:55.200 --> 49:56.519
Are you sure?

49:56.700 --> 49:57.689
Mm.

49:58.570 --> 49:59.696
Very sure.

49:59.870 --> 50:01.735
Well, you seem to have gotten away.

50:02.250 --> 50:03.114
Yeah.

50:03.910 --> 50:04.899
This time.

50:06.540 --> 50:08.747
All right, even if Shannon did attack you,

50:08.920 --> 50:11.161
I have to believe
that it was something he...

50:11.420 --> 50:13.661
Might have instigated on his own.

50:14.420 --> 50:17.139
Either way, it...
Doesn't make a difference.

50:20.560 --> 50:21.458
You know...

50:21.930 --> 50:26.594
My brother's a very
black and white kind of guy.

50:27.480 --> 50:30.142
Something's either true... Or it isn't.

50:31.230 --> 50:34.028
I'm a little more... Open.

50:37.610 --> 50:38.565
Meaning?

50:41.950 --> 50:44.748
You look like Danny Rand.

50:45.250 --> 50:46.365
Danny Rand is dead.

50:48.250 --> 50:49.990
Maybe the truth is somewhere in between.

50:51.460 --> 50:55.044
"If you wish to see the truth...
Then hold no opinions."

50:57.970 --> 50:59.335
It's a Zen saying.

51:02.100 --> 51:03.089
Okay.

51:06.180 --> 51:08.592
So, then...

51:09.520 --> 51:10.930
I guess I should call you Danny?

51:11.110 --> 51:12.099
Yeah.

51:13.440 --> 51:14.429
Please.

51:14.820 --> 51:17.641
All right, Danny. You said you had some
questions for me.

51:18.610 --> 51:20.942
I'm not sure I'm gonna be able to answer
all of them, but...

51:21.120 --> 51:22.109
I'll do my best.

51:22.660 --> 51:25.993
I have a lot of questions, too.
Why don't you go first?

51:29.290 --> 51:32.874
It's... It's all kind of crazy.

51:34.210 --> 51:36.201
I don't even know where to start.

51:37.010 --> 51:39.001
